Description: Defines S4 classes for storing data for spatial experiments.
    Main examples are reported by using seqFISH and 10x-Visium Spatial Gene 
    Expression data. 
    This includes specialized methods for storing, retrieving 
    spatial coordinates, 10x dedicated parameters and their handling.
